ation on a mobile (or GPS) device of your choice.</p>\r\n[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"single\" top_margin=\"40\" bottom_margin=\"40\" sep_color=\"#096faf\" border_size=\"2px\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][/one_half][/fullwidth]','What We Do','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-revision-v1','','','2016-05-05 15:39:09','2016-05-05 15:39:09','',4,'http://fws.dev/?p=352',0,'revision','',0);
