tic-mountain-lake-in-canada-moraine-lake-in-alberta-canada-316951322.jpg\" alt=\"\" />[/imageframe][/one_half][one_half last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"solid\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"down\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][separator style_type=\"single\" top_margin=\"40\" bottom_margin=\"35px\" sep_color=\"#096faf\" border_size=\"2px\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\r\n<p class=\"description\">Brian Fulfrost and Associates are recognized experts in GIS database development, spatial data modeling, and (2D/3D) cartographic visualization. Our team of GIS analysts has platform expertise with ESRI products (ArcGIS 10.x, ArcSDE, ArcGIS Server, geodatabases, network analyst, spatial analyst, 3D analyst) as well as Open Source platforms (GeoServer, PostGreSQL, OpenLayers, PostGIS, Leaflet, GeoExt, R, etc. )</p>\r\n<p class=\"description\">Additionally, Brian Fulfrost has over 15 years experience teaching GIS and Remote Sensing to a range of professionals, students and researchers. Building on this experience, BFA can tailor the development of in-person or online GIS trainings to suit your organization\'s needs.</p>\r\n[/fusion_text][/one_half][/fullwidth][fullwidth background_color=\"\" background_image=\"http://fws.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/forest3-1024x401.jpg\" background_parallax=\"fixed\" enable_mobile=\"no\" parallax_speed=\"0.3\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" video_url=\"\" video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_color=\"\" over